{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RwDqvCiDFpH9uU7WaF1JnE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Add `@compodoc/compodoc` `^1.1.26` to root `package.json` devDependencies and run `npm install` to pin it explicitly rather than relying on the transitive resolution.\n2. Flip `\"compodoc\": false` to `\"compodoc\": true` on both `storybook` and `build-storybook` targets in `packages/ngx-smart-components/project.json`; leave `compodocArgs` unset to accept the `[\"-e\", \"json\"]` default.\n3. Create `packages/ngx-smart-components/.storybook/tsconfig.doc.json` extending `./tsconfig.json` with `\"include\": [\"../src/**/*.ts\"]` and `\"exclude\": [\"../**/*.spec.ts\", \"../**/*.stories.ts\"]` so compodoc analyzes only library sources.\n4. Add `\"@compodoc/documentation\"` to the `addons` array in `.storybook/main.ts` to render the generated JSON as the Docs tab.\n5. Run `npm exec nx storybook ngx-smart-components` and confirm `documentation.json` is generated under the configDir and the Docs tab shows component metadata."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a734b927635d23dac (use SendMessage with to: 'a734b927635d23dac' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 19141\ntool_uses: 0\nduration_ms: 6190</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e114d311-283b-4023-9652-1abc0ea4446e","uuid":"a35fb941-9545-47cd-88f3-146dd9661eb8","timestamp":"2026-04-24T07:59:35.120Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"## Task\n\n> Add Compodoc to the Storybook for ngx-smart-components using the Nx docs guide.\n\n## Orientation Findings\n\n1. Project is an Nx 22.6.5 monorepo with a single library `ngx-smart-components` in `packages/ngx-smart-components/`.\n2. Storybook 10.3.5 (`@storybook/angular`) is installed. Both `storybook` and `build-storybook` Nx targets exist in `project.json` with `\"compodoc\": false`.\n3. `@compodoc/compodoc` 1.2.1 is already installed as a transitive dependency -- NOT listed in roo